Version:  1.0
Type:     game/think

GlufsMines is another little multitasking minesweeper clone for Amiga.

Feautures:

 - Nice design
 - 3 different levels
 - Choose your own grid size
 - Saved highscore
 - Alot more...

Postcardware, author wants you to send him postcard if you like the game.

Released: 01-Jan-97
